    dc:description "Figures 1–8: adults. 1, Marplena designina, holotype, ♂, RSA (©NHMUK); 2, Ibidem, paratype, ♀, RSA (©NHMUK); 3, Ibidem, ♂, RSA (MFN); 4, Ibidem, ♀, RSA (MFN); 5, Watsonopsestis smithi sp. n. holotype, ♂, Tanzania (ANHRT); 6, Ibidem, paratype, ♂, Tanzania (RCAK); 7, Ibidem, paratype, ♀, (©NHMUK); 8, Ibidem, paratype, ♀, RSA (©NHMUK)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6412890/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6412898>
    dc:description "Figures 19–25. Male genitalia. 19, Marplena designina, holotype, gen. slide No. BM Thyatiridae 259 (©NHMUK); 20, Watsonopsestis smithi sp. n., holotype, gen. slide No. LG 5749 (ANHRT); 21, Ibidem, paratype, gen. slide No. LG 5630 (RCAK); 22, Aethiopsestis austrina, holotype, gen. slide No. BM Thyatiridae 196 (©NHMUK); 23, Ibidem, paratype, gen. slide No. BM Thyatiridae 1 (©NHMUK); 24, A. nebulosa, holotype, gen. slide No. BM Thyatiridae 3 (©NHMUK); 25, Ibidem, paratype, gen. slide No. BM Thyatiridae 38 (©NHMUK)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6412898/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6412902>
    dc:description "Figures 30–34. Female genitalia. 30, Marplena designina, paratype, gen. slide No. BM Thyatiridae 260 (©NHMUK); 31, Watsonopsestis smithi sp. n., paratype, gen. slide No. BM Thyatiridae 195 (©NHMUK); 32, Aethiopsestis austrina, paratype, gen. slide No. BM Thyatiridae 41 (©NHMUK); 33, A. nebulosa, paratype, gen. slide No. BM Thyatiridae 39 (©NHMUK); 34, A. mufindiae, gen. slide No. LG 5628 (ANHRT)." ;
